程序包 org.example

类 DataStreamHandle

java.lang.Object
org.example.DataStreamHandle
public class DataStreamHandle extends Object
DataStreamHandle class is responsible for requesting data from the Alpha Vantage API, process the data, call the Median Selection class to obtain the relevant median, and then process the data into the format required by JFreeChart.
